---
// src/components/SecStrength.astro
---
<section class="sec s-strength">
  <div class="ab-strength-section">
    <div class="ab-strength-bg"></div>

    <!-- 상단 헤더 -->
    <div class="ab-strength-header">
      <p class="ab-str-sub fade-up">설계·구축만 잘하는 회사는 있을 수 있습니다</p>
      <h2 class="ab-str-headline fade-up fade-up-d1">
        하지만 이담에스티는<br>
        <em>설계·구축만</em> 잘하지 않습니다
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- 장점 카드 4개 -->
    <div class="ab-str-grid">

      <!-- 철저한 유지보수 -->
      <div class="ab-str-card fade-up fade-up-d1">
        <div class="ab-str-icon">
          <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- 렌치 몸통 -->
            <path d="M38 10c-5.5 0-10 4.5-10 10 0 1.4.3 2.7.8 3.9L14 38.7A4 4 0 0014 44.4l5.6 5.6a4 4 0 005.7 0L40 35.2c1.2.5 2.5.8 3.9.8 5.5 0 10-4.5 10-10a10 10 0 00-1.2-4.8l-5.8 5.8-4-1-1-4 5.8-5.8A10 10 0 0038 10z" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.06)"/>
            <!-- 체크 표시 -->
            <circle cx="20" cy="44" r="3" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.1)" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="ab-str-title">철저한 유지보수</h4>
        <p class="ab-str-desc">구축 후에도 끝까지 책임집니다. 신속한 AS와 정기 점검으로 시스템을 안정적으로 유지합니다.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 투명한 견적 -->
      <div class="ab-str-card fade-up fade-up-d2">
        <div class="ab-str-icon">
          <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- 문서 -->
            <rect x="14" y="10" width="30" height="38" rx="3" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.06)"/>
            <!-- 줄 -->
            <line x1="21" y1="20" x2="37" y2="20" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="21" y1="27" x2="37" y2="27" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="21" y1="34" x2="30" y2="34" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- 돋보기 -->
            <circle cx="43" cy="43" r="9" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.06)"/>
            <line x1="49.5" y1="49.5" x2="55" y2="55" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- 원 안 체크 -->
            <path d="M40 43l2.5 2.5 4-4" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="ab-str-title">투명한 견적</h4>
        <p class="ab-str-desc">예상치 못한 추가 비용 없이 명확하고 투명한 견적으로 신뢰할 수 있는 파트너십을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 일정 준수 -->
      <div class="ab-str-card fade-up fade-up-d3">
        <div class="ab-str-icon">
          <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- 달력 외곽 -->
            <rect x="10" y="14" width="44" height="40" rx="4" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.06)"/>
            <!-- 상단 바 -->
            <rect x="10" y="14" width="44" height="12" rx="4" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.12)" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2"/>
            <!-- 핀 2개 -->
            <line x1="22" y1="10" x2="22" y2="18" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="42" y1="10" x2="42" y2="18" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- 체크 -->
            <path d="M20 38l7 7 17-17" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="ab-str-title">일정 준수</h4>
        <p class="ab-str-desc">17년간 쌓아온 노하우로 프로젝트 일정을 철저히 관리합니다. 약속한 날짜는 반드시 지킵니다.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 검증된 퀄리티 -->
      <div class="ab-str-card fade-up fade-up-d4">
        <div class="ab-str-icon">
          <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- 방패 -->
            <path d="M32 8L12 16v16c0 11 9 20 20 24 11-4 20-13 20-24V16L32 8z" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="rgba(26,47,138,0.06)"/>
            <!-- 내부 체크 -->
            <path d="M22 32l7 7 13-13" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="ab-str-title">검증된 퀄리티</h4>
        <p class="ab-str-desc">516개 이상의 구축 사례가 증명합니다. 공공기관부터 방송국까지 신뢰받는 17년의 기술력입니다.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- 마무리 메시지 -->
    <div class="ab-message fade-up fade-up-d2">
      <div class="ab-message-inner">
        <!-- 위 따옴표 -->
        <svg class="ab-quote-top" width="52" height="40" viewBox="0 0 52 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M0 40V24.8C0 15.467 4.267 8.267 12.8 3.2L16 8C12.267 10.133 9.867 13.067 8.8 16.8H16V40H0ZM28 40V24.8C28 15.467 32.267 8.267 40.8 3.2L44 8C40.267 10.133 37.867 13.067 36.8 16.8H44V40H28Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
        </svg>

        <p class="ab-msg-text">
          이담에스티는 다양한 미디어 시스템 구축 노하우와<br>
          끊임없는 사내 연구 및 대외 기술 습득 활동을 통해<br>
          <strong>트렌디한 구축 서비스</strong>를 제공하겠습니다.
        </p>
        <div class="ab-msg-sig">— 이담에스티 임직원 일동</div>

        <!-- 아래 따옴표 -->
        <svg class="ab-quote-bot" width="52" height="40" viewBox="0 0 52 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M0 40V24.8C0 15.467 4.267 8.267 12.8 3.2L16 8C12.267 10.133 9.867 13.067 8.8 16.8H16V40H0ZM28 40V24.8C28 15.467 32.267 8.267 40.8 3.2L44 8C40.267 10.133 37.867 13.067 36.8 16.8H44V40H28Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ab-strength-section {
    position: relative;
    background: #fff;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ab-strength-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/strength-bg.jpg');
    background-size: cover; background-position: center;
    filter: brightness(0.65) saturate(0.7);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ab-strength-section::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(240,244,255,0.68);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  /* 자식 요소들 z-index 올리기 */
  .ab-strength-header,
  .ab-str-grid,
  .ab-message { position: relative; z-index: 3; }

  /* 헤더 */
  .ab-strength-header {
    text-align: center; padding: 96px 48px 64px;
    max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .ab-str-sub {
    font-size: 16px; color: #6b7a8d;
    margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .ab-str-headline {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.2vw, 50px); font-weight: 900;
    color: #0D1F2D; line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }
  .ab-str-headline em { font-style: normal; color: #1a2f8a; }

  /* 카드 4개 */
  .ab-str-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px 80px;
  }
  .ab-str-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    padding: 40px 32px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,47,138,0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,47,138,0.08), 0 2px 8px rgba(26,47,138,0.04);
    transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .ab-str-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border-color: rgba(26,47,138,0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(26,47,138,0.14), 0 4px 16px rgba(26,47,138,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }
  .ab-str-icon { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .ab-str-title {
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #0D1F2D;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .ab-str-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #6b7a8d; line-height: 1.9; }

  /* 마무리 메시지 */
  .ab-message {
    position: relative; z-index: 3;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
  }
  .ab-message-inner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1a3a 0%, #1a2f8a 100%);
    padding: 64px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ab-message-inner::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 0px, rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 1px,
      transparent 1px, transparent 60px
    );
  }
  .ab-quote-top {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .ab-quote-bot {
    display: block;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }
  .ab-msg-text {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 22px);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .ab-msg-text strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ab-msg-text strong::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -2px;
    height: 2px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .ab-msg-sig {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    position: relative;
  }


  /* ── 반응형 ── */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .ab-str-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .ab-block { padding: 0 32px; }
    .ab-section-sep { margin: 0 32px; }
    .ab-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; padding-top: 60px; padding-bottom: 60px; }
    .ab-row-reverse .ab-media-col { order: 0; }
    .ab-video { max-width: 360px; }
    .ab-strength-header { padding: 72px 32px 48px; }
    .ab-str-grid { padding: 0 32px 60px; gap: 16px; }
    .ab-message { padding: 24px 32px 60px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .ab-block { padding: 0 20px; }
    .ab-section-sep { margin: 0 20px; }
    .ab-str-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 0 20px 48px; }
    .ab-str-card { padding: 28px 24px; }
    .ab-strength-header { padding: 56px 20px 40px; }
    .ab-message { padding: 16px 20px 48px; }
  }

  .s-strength { display: block; }
</style>
